@node "WhatIsIT?" "What Is SuperIT ?"
@next "Installation"
@prev "Main"
@{b}--(( What Is SuperIT ? ))--@{ub}

SuperIT is a VERY addictive game that we, @{"3AMIGOS Software" link "About 3AMIGOS" 0}, created during MAY/JUNE 1997. The idea of the game came from when we use to play IT with our mates at school, as many of you may also remember. In SuperIT, when you are IT you have a disease, and this can be seen by the dots that will appear over your character's body. The aim of the game is to try and get rid of the disease before the time runs out and you lose. This is done by chasing the other characters around the screen, trying to pass the disease onto them so that they become IT, which means that they have to chase everyone and so on...

The game took about a month to do and is both graphically and musically well presented (so we think!). The game was programmed in AMOS 1.3, and the hardest part was trying to create the artificial intelligence for the computer to chase the other characters.

