@node "Installation" "Installation"
@next "Requirements"
@prev "WhatIsIT?"
@{b}--(( Installation ))--@{ub}

To install SuperIT just double click on the SuperIT-Install icon and follow the on-screen instructions. However, if a problem occurs, or you do not have the installer executable, then you can install it manually. See below:

1. Create a drawer on your harddisk where you want to put SuperIT.

2. Label it 'SuperIT' and make an assign to it in your user-startup.

3. E.g.  Assign >NIL: SuperIT: DH1:SuperIT

4. Double click on the SuperIT disk icon and select 'Show All Files'.

5. Copy the contents of the disk to your newly created drawer.

6. In the Libs drawer copy the 'Mathtrans.Library' to your SYS:LIBS/

7. The version supplied is 37.1, so check to see if you have a later version.

8. If you have, you do not need to copy the supplied library across.

9. Reboot your AMIGA to play the wonderful SuperIT!

10. Have Fun!!
@endnode

